Game.....: Fatal Fury - Mark Of The Wolves
Origin...: USA - NTSC
Released.: November 23rd, 2001
Ripped.......: Nothing

Terry Bogard returns to defend his crown as the King of Fighters. Part of the SNK 2D Fighting Series, Fatal Fury: Mark of the Wolves keeps the legend alive!

Game Features:
- 11 All-new characters including Rock Howard, son of legendary warrior Geese Howard!
- 3 New Modes to boost gameplay - Offensive, Defensive and Tactical!
- Unlock Super Moves and Hidden Abilities for each fighter!
- Break an opponent's attack to use their special fighting energy against them!